descripcion: In this open-world, single-player or co-op survival adventure, craft weapons and armor, build your base, and traverse the playground on your buggy.
plataforma: Xbox One, Xbox Series S, Xbox Series X

descripcion: Super Meat Boy 3D is a tough-as-nails platformer where you play as an animated cube of meat who's trying to save his girlfriend, Bandage Girl, from the evil Dr. Fetus. Dash through deadly traps, wall-jump across brutal levels, and die — a lot — in this fast-paced, precision-based adventure now reimagined in full 3D.
plataforma: Xbox One, Xbox Series S, Xbox Series X

descripcion: Little Nightmares III is a disturbing atmospheric adventure in which the close friends Low and Alone, who wish to escape the Nothingness, will work together to survive a world full of nightmares and uncover its dark secrets.

An intergalactic conspiracy threatens the fate of humanity! Team up with a wide cast of talking alien guns as you shoot, stab, and skate your way through bizarre worlds, deadly enemies, and absurd missions in this hilarious and action-packed sequel to the hit game High On Life.
plataforma: Xbox Series S, Xbox Series X

descripcion: Face your fears in Resident Evil: Requiem — a new chapter of survival horror where every bullet counts and every shadow hides a threat.
plataforma: Xbox Series S, Xbox Series X

descripcion: Experience a new era of crime in GTA VI — a sprawling open-world adventure full of danger, chaos, and limitless possibilities.
